data.description: Located in a quaint neighborhood in the small town of Red Bluff, this property gives you the perfect opportunity to own your own home. Inside you will find beautiful original hardwood flooring, shiplap accent wall giving off the favored farmhouse feel and a spacious living area that features a perfectly positioned fireplace surrounded by brick. The kitchen is equipped with tile countertops, numerous cabinets for all your pots and pans and a gas range that will make your culinary experience a piece of cake. When it’s time to decompress, all 3 bedrooms offer plenty of room to stretch your legs while the bathroom creates an ideal setting for your morning routine with its tiled shower. Other amenities include ceiling fans throughout, built-ins for extra storage, low-cost solar lease to help with energy costs, an attached 1 car garage and much more! The fully fenced backyard awaits. It gives you raised garden beds with sprinklers so you can cultivate your own garden and loads of room to barbeque with friends, play a game of catch or let your furry friends' roam. Don’t miss your chance to become a homeowner with this great property!
